{"word":"κόπος","slug":"κόπος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κόπος</b></el> <el>(κόπος, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κόπτω'><el>κόπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a striking, beating</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>toil, trouble, suffering</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>weariness, fatigue</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}